<section class="hero">
  <span class="hero__eyebrow">Privacy</span>
  <h1 class="hero__title">How Voxlane handles account, billing, and app data.</h1>
  <p class="hero__copy">
    Voxlane uses its own account system for identity, Stripe for billing, and its backend for entitlement and device records.
  </p>
</section>

<section class="section-card">
  <ul style="margin-top: 12px;">
    <li>Account login is handled directly by Voxlane using Google OAuth or email and password.</li>
    <li>Subscription checkout and billing management are handled through Stripe-hosted pages.</li>
    <li>The backend stores user, entitlement, subscription, and device metadata needed to operate the service.</li>
    <li>Direct macOS updates are delivered through Sparkle using the signed appcast published on voxlane.io.</li>
    <li>For privacy questions, contact <a href="mailto:<%= AppConfig.support_email %>"><%= AppConfig.support_email %></a>.</li>
  </ul>
</section>
